Title: AN ACT PROVIDING FOR THE PURCHASE, OUT OF THE FUNDS APPROPRIATED FOR THE BUREAU OF EDUCATION BY ACT NUMBERED NINETEEN HUNDRED AND NINETY-TWO, OF ADDITIONAL LAND FOR THE INDUSTRIAL SCHOOL RESERVATION AT BAGUIO.
Data:
[ Act No. 2002, December 08, 1910 ]
AN ACT PROVIDING FOR THE PURCHASE, OUT OF THE FUNDS APPROPRIATED FOR THE BUREAU OF EDUCATION BY ACT NUMBERED NINETEEN HUNDRED AND NINETY-TWO, OF ADDITIONAL LAND FOR THE INDUSTRIAL SCHOOL RESERVATION AT BAGUIO.
By authority of the United States, be it enacted by the Philippine Commission, that:
Section 1. The funds appropriated by Act Numbered Nineteen hundred and ninety-two for the Bureau of Education are hereby made available in an amount not to exceed one thousand pesos for the purchase of in the city of Baguio, subprovince of Benguet, Mountain Province.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect on its passage.1a—àphi1
Enacted, December 8, 1910.
